claim.claim-text:
45. A device for dispensing a predetermined volume of liquid, the device comprising: 
a source of pressurized liquid; 
an expandable chamber; 
an metering valve which may be moved between a first position and a second position, the metering valve including a discharge opening, wherein in the first position liquid flows from the source to the expandable chamber to expand and fill the chamber with a predetermined unit volume of liquid, and in the second position the unit volume of liquid flows from the chamber to the discharge opening.
